title: FIVE YEARS In The Making
body_text:
DODGEBALL 20. DODGEBALL 50. DODGEBALL 100. DODGEBALL 150. 1st, 2nd, 3rd, and 4th Anniversaries. Maybe the biggest one of them all remains.
On
September 11, 2010
,
EastCoastDodgeball
reaches its prestigious
5 Year Anniversary
and you can bet legendary figures of the sport and their supportive families will come together in celebration. Your attendance at this once-in-a-lifetime extravaganza would be greatly appreciated and certainly rewarding. Special start time is at 5:30pm.
body_html:
DODGEBALL 20. DODGEBALL 50. DODGEBALL 100. DODGEBALL 150. 1st, 2nd, 3rd, and 4th Anniversaries. Maybe the biggest one of them all remains.

On September 11, 2010, EastCoastDodgeball reaches its prestigious 5 Year Anniversary and you can bet legendary figures of the sport and their supportive families will come together in celebration. Your attendance at this once-in-a-lifetime extravaganza would be greatly appreciated and certainly rewarding. Special start time is at 5:30pm.
